    <title>Decision Transformer: Reinforcement Learning
      via Sequence Modeling</title>
    <summary>  We introduce a framework that abstracts reinforcement learning as a
sequence modeling problem.  This allows us to draw upon the simplicity and
scalability of the Transformer architecture.
</summary>
